abstract: Fourteen-year-old Memphis boy is charged as juvenile with attempted murder and child abuse after attacking three children, one of whom died.
lead_paragraph: The Memphis police say a 14-year-old boy attacked three children, one of whom died, and has been charged as a juvenile with attempted murder and child abuse.

headline.main: Tennessee: Boy, 14, Charged in Death of Girl, 6
